### Teacher Detail API - Get teacher with class assignments information
### This API returns complete teacher information including all classes they are assigned to

@teacherServiceUrl = http://localhost:5000

### 1. Create Teacher with Assignments (for testing)
# @name createTeacherWithClasses
POST {{teacherServiceUrl}}/api/teachers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Nguyen Van",
  "lastName": "Detail",
  "email": "nguyenvandetail@school.edu.vn",
  "phone": "0909111222",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-06-15",
  "address": "123 Teacher Street, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City",
  "assignments": [
    {
      "classId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
      "role": "Homeroom Teacher"
    },
    {
      "classId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
      "role": "Subject Teacher"
    }
  ]
}

###

### 2. Get Teacher Detail by ID (with class information)
# Replace {teacherId} with actual ID from create response
# @name getTeacherDetail
GET {{teacherServiceUrl}}/api/teachers/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Accept: application/json

###

